# Files in this repo that pre-date the chezmoi migration. Chezmoi treats any
# source file without a recognized prefix as a target rooted at $HOME, so
# without these ignores it would try to write LICENSE → ~/LICENSE, etc.
# Listed in target form (chezmoi.io/reference/special-files-and-directories/chezmoiignore/).

LICENSE
README.md
